==Hebrew script==
===Letter===
'''ש''' (spelled ''[[shin]]'') is the twenty-first letter of the [[Hebrew]] alphabet.
:'''שׁ''' is shin, representing /ʃ/, /S/
:'''שׂ''' is sin, representing /s/

ש also represents the [[numeral]] 300 in Hebrew numbering.

* '''Last''': [[ר]]
* '''Next''': [[ת]]

